}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== Despite being a 7-Port USB hub and having an external power jack, this thing does not come with a power adapter..
This device uses two '''Alcor Micro''' 4-Port USB Hub controllers (presumably AU6254). The device presents itself as two seperate 058f:6254 USB hubs to the host system.
